## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the inherent challenges in defining and measuring the impact of terrorism. The complexity of terrorism as a phenomenon means that its effects can vary significantly across different contexts and regions. Additionally, the rapidly changing nature of terrorist tactics and strategies requires continuous monitoring and analysis to fully understand its evolving threats.